'''拓扑绝缘体'''是一种内部绝缘，界面允许电荷移动的材料。

在拓扑绝缘体的内部，电子[[能带结构|能带结构]]和常规的[[絕緣體|绝缘体]]相似，其[[费米能|费米能级]]位于[[导带|导带]]和[[价带|价带]]之间。在拓扑绝缘体的表面存在一些特殊的量子态，这些量子态位于块体能带结构的带隙之中，从而允许导电。这些量子态可以用类似[[拓扑学|拓扑学]]中的[[亏格|亏格]]的整数表征，是{{le|拓扑序|Topological order}}的一个特例<ref>{{Cite journal
| last = Kane | first = C. L.  | coauthors = Mele, E. J.  | date = 30 September 2005 
| title = Z<sub>2</sub> Topological Order and the Quantum Spin Hall Effect
| journal = [[Physical_Review_Letters|Physical Review Letters]] | volume = 95 | issue = 14 | pages = 146802
| doi = 10.1103/PhysRevLett.95.146802
| url = http://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevLett.95.146802
}}</ref>。

==预言和发现==
拓扑保护的边缘状态（一维）在[[碲化汞|碲化汞]]/[[碲化镉|碲化镉]][[量子阱|量子阱]]中被预言于1987年<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1126/science.1133734 | pmid = 17170299 | volume = 314 | issue = 5806 | pages = 1757–1761 | last = Bernevig | first = B. Andrei | coauthors = Taylor L. Hughes, Shou-Cheng Zhang | title = Quantum Spin Hall Effect and Topological Phase Transition in HgTe Quantum Wells | journal = Science | accessdate = 2010-03-25 | date = 2006-12-15 | url = http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/314/5806/1757 | archive-date = 2008-06-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080617152948/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/314/5806/1757 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，随后于2007年由实验观测证实<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1126/science.1148047 | pmid = 17885096 | volume = 318 | issue = 5851 | pages = 766–770 | last = Konig | first = Markus | coauthors = Steffen Wiedmann, Christoph Brune, Andreas Roth, Hartmut Buhmann, Laurens W. Molenkamp, Xiao-Liang Qi, Shou-Cheng Zhang | title = Quantum Spin Hall Insulator State in HgTe Quantum Wells | journal = Science | accessdate = 2010-03-25 | date = 2007-11-02 | url = http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/318/5851/766 | archive-date = 2010-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100511220233/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/318/5851/766 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。很快，拓扑绝缘体又被预言存在于含铋的二元化合物三维固体中<ref>{{Cite journal
| doi = 10.1103/PhysRevB.76.045302 | volume = 76 | issue = 4 | pages = 045302 | last = Fu | first = Liang | coauthors = C. L. Kane
| title = Topological insulators with inversion symmetry
| journal = Physical Review B | accessdate = 2010-03-26 | date = 2007-07-02
| url = http://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevB.76.045302
}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal
| doi = 10.1088/1367-2630/9/9/356 | issn = 1367-2630 | volume = 9 | issue = 9 | pages = 356–356 | last = Shuichi Murakami
|title = Phase transition between the quantum spin Hall and insulator phases in 3D: emergence of a topological gapless phase
| journal = New Journal of Physics | accessdate = 2010-03-26 | date = 2007
| url = http://iopscience.iop.org/1367-2630/9/9/356/
}}</ref>。第一个实验实现的三维拓扑绝缘体在锑化铋中被观察到<ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1038/nature06843 | last = Hsieh | first = D. | coauthors = D. Qian, L. Wray, Y. Xia, Y. S. Hor, R. J. Cava & M. Z. Hasan | title = A Topological Dirac insulator in a 3D quantum spin Hall phase | journal = Nature | volume = 452 | issue = 9 | pages = 970–974 | accessdate = 2010 | date = 2008 | url = http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v452/n7190/full/nature06843.html | pmid = 18432240 | archive-date = 2009-12-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091223022215/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v452/n7190/full/nature06843.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，随后不同实验组又通过[[角分辨光电子谱|角分辨光电子谱]]的方法，在锑，碲化铋，硒化铋，碲化锑中观察到了拓扑保护的表面量子态<ref>{{Cite journal | last = Hasan | first = M. Z | coauthors = C. L Kane | title = Topological Insulators | journal = 1002.3895 | accessdate = 2010-04-27 | date = 2010-02-20 | url = http://arxiv.org/abs/1002.3895 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308200803/https://arxiv.org/abs/1002.3895 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。现在人们相信，在其他一些材料体系中，也存在拓扑绝缘态<ref>{{Cite journal
| doi = 10.1038/nmat2771 | pmid = 20512153 | issn = 1476-1122| volume = 9 | issue = 7 | pages = 546–549
| last = Lin | first = Hsin | coauthors = L. Andrew Wray, Yuqi Xia, Suyang Xu, Shuang Jia, Robert J. Cava, Arun Bansil, M. Zahid Hasan
|title = Half-Heusler ternary compounds as new multifunctional experimental platforms for topological quantum phenomena
| journal = Nat Mater | accessdate = 2010-08-05 | date = 2010-07
