| title = Observation of Time-Reversal-Protected Single-Dirac-Cone Topological-Insulator States in Bi2Te3 and Sb2Te3
| url = http://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevLett.103.146401 | accessdate = 2010-03-25
}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal
| doi = 10.1209/0295-5075/81/57006| volume = 81| issue = 5| pages = 57006
